high_descs: Turn around to face the island.
Pick up the potato in front of the tea pot on the island.
Take the potato and turn left to go to the sink.
Place the potato in the sink and turn the water on, then off. Take the potato out of the sink.
Take the potato and turn around and then left to find the microwave.
Place the potato inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Wash and then cook a potato.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the counter.
Pick the potato up from the counter.
Go left and stand in front of the sink.
Put the potato in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick up the potato.
Turn and cross the room and go left to stand in front of the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Turn left and walk towards the sink.
Place the potato in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn around, walk towards the wall, and then turn left towards the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed potato in the microwave.
